Description:
    Create a new siade v3 API

Example:
    bin/rails generate scaffold_resource MDS::Effectifs
    bin/rails generate scaffold_resource [provider]::[resource_name] [options]

Options:
    --api-kind=particulier       # Create resources for APIParticulier instead of APIEntreprise (default is APIEntreprise)
    --document=true              # Add support for document uploader (default is false)
    --validation-type=siren      # Params for validation: siren, siret, civility, custom (default is siren)
    --with-france-connect=true   # Add an additional controller with France Connect support (only for APIParticulier)
    --verb=POST                  # Use POST instead of GET for the HTTP request (default is GET)
    --prochainement=true         # Prepare the documentation and staging without a working API (default is false)
    --is-collection=true         # Return a collection instead of a single resource (default is false)

Examples:

API Entreprise, validation with SIRET in Prochainement mode:
      bin/rails generate scaffold_resource CNAV::PrimeActivite --prochainement=true --validation-type=siret

API Particulier with France Connect and civility:
      bin/rails generate scaffold_resource CNOUS::StudentScholarship --api-kind=particulier --with-france-connect=true --validation-type=civility

